    SelectItem

    Expression Extends:

    class SelectItem extends BaseComponent(HTMLElement)

    Mixin Extends:

    HTMLElement, BaseComponent

    A Select item component

    See:

    • ../examples/#select

    Example:

    Markup

    JS constructor
    new Coral.Select.Item();

    Public Members

    public content: * source

    null

    public disabled: Boolean source

    Whether this item is disabled. When set to true, this will prevent every user interaction with the item. If disabled is set to true for a selected item it will be deselected.

    • false by default.
    • reflected

    public selected: Boolean source

    Whether the item is selected. Selected cannot be set to true if the item is disabled.

    • false by default.
    • reflected

    public trackingElement: * source

    Inherited from BaseComponent#trackingElement.

    public value: String source

    Value of the item. If not explicitly set, the value of Node.textContent is returned.

    • "" by default.
    • reflected
